<b>Topology for Computing</b><br>
Afra Zomorodian<br>
Cambridge Monographs on Applied and Computational Mathematics (No. 16)<br>
<br>
<a href = "http://www.cambridge.org/catalogue/catalogue.asp?isbn=0521836662">
Cambridge Catalogue</a><br>
<a href = "http://books.google.com/books?id=oKEGGMgnWKcC">Google
  Book Search</a> <img src = "images/new.gif"><br>
<a href = "http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/tg/detail/-/0521836662/qid=1104185117/sr=8-1/ref=sr_8_xs_ap_i1_xgl14/102-3479416-4472923?v=glance&s=books&n=507846">
Amazon</a><br>
